he told a boatload of journalists he was swimming to protest the 
rivers pollution and express confidence in the future of the tagus 
earlier he announced proposals for a 170 million development 
project for lisbons waterfront 
the tagus runs into the atlantic ocean about 20 miles west of 
lisbon deepwater port facilities on both sides of the river are of 
major economic importance to the lisbon area 
