the climate of fear and distrust within the generic drug 
industry it said was created by a house investigations subcommittee 
because of the fraudulent deeds of a few 
to win fda approval of generic drugs manufacturers must submit 
them for tests by independent laboratories 
the post quoted pharmakinetics officials as saying they became 
