things 
i think menem is the only way to save the country said 
ricardo gutierrez a suit salesman who also did not vote for menem 
the publicservice price increases have narrowed an unsustainable 
budget deficit while a 54 percent devaluation has stabilized the 
austral currency and brought down interest rates 
wage and price guidelines have cooled hyperinflation while the 
cost of living rose by 197 percent in july the rate for august is 
projected at 35 percent and for september at 10 percent or less 
