comparison to sale prices but that the items actually were never 
available at the higher prices 
when the district attorneys office brought the problems to our 
attention we took steps immediately to make sure it doesnt happen 
again nordstrom spokeswoman chris breidenbaugh said in the 
future we will be careful to be as specific as we can the 
charges stemmed from sales ads from last october and december 
